        </p>
      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec53-7">
        <p>
          For the sequence <m>a_1 ,a_2 , \ldots ,a_n , \ldots</m> , assume that <m>a_1 = 1</m>,
          <m>a_2 = 1</m>, and that for each <m>n \in \mathbb{N}</m>,
          <m>a_{n + 2} = \dfrac{1}{2}\left( {a_{n + 1} + \dfrac{2}{{a_n }}} \right)</m>.
