      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec53-8">
        <p>
          For the sequence   <m>a_1 ,a_2 , \ldots ,a_n , \ldots</m>,
          assume that <m>a_1=1</m>, <m>a_2=1</m>,
          <m>a_3=1</m>, and for that each natural number <m>n</m>,
